docs {
  # List Saved Views

  Returns user-saved chart views with specific system selections and filters.

  ## Data Shape

  ```json
  [
    {
      "id": "view-001",
      "userId": "user-001",
      "name": "System 1 vs System 2 Comparison",
      "chartConfigurationId": "chart-interactivity",
      "selectedSystems": ["system1", "system2"],
      "filters": {
        "modelId": "deepseek-r1",
        "division": "closed"
      },
      "normalization": {
        "enabled": false,
        "overrides": {}
      },
      "layers": [],
      "createdAt": "2026-01-20T14:30:00Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-01-20T14:30:00Z"
    }
  ]
  ```

  ## Fields

  | Field | Type | Description |
  |-------|------|-------------|
  | id | string | Unique view identifier |
  | userId | string | Owner user ID |
  | name | string | User-defined view name |
  | chartConfigurationId | string | Base chart configuration |
  | selectedSystems | array | System IDs to display |
  | filters | object | Active filter settings |
  | normalization | object | Normalization settings with overrides |
  | layers | array | Additional data layers to display |
  | createdAt | string | ISO 8601 creation timestamp |
  | updatedAt | string | ISO 8601 last update timestamp |

  ## Normalization Object

  ```json
  {
    "enabled": true,
    "overrides": {
      "system2": 0.5
    }
  }
  ```

  Allows per-system normalization factor overrides.
}
